2015-07~07
http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/security/620700/government-defends-uighur-rendition-security

Bangkok Post
China's official state TV mouthpiece broadcast video and commentary claiming the 109 Uighurs forced aboard this rendition flight from Songkhla last week were all terrorist suspects, and were handcuffed and hooded for the flight.
The Uighurs, each accompanied by a guard, were those handed over to China by the government last week after secret negotiations that have brought worldwide criticism.

